<h2 align="center"><b>THE ROAD TO ELEUSIS</b></h2>

<h5 align="center">Unveiling the Secret of the Mysteries</h5>

<p align="center">R. Gordon Wasson </p>

<p align="center">Albert Hofmann </p>

<p align="center">Carl A. P. Ruck </p>

<p align="center">HARCOURT BRACE JOVANOVICH </p>

<p align="center">New York and London </p>

<p align="center">Copyright 1978 by Harcourt Brace Jovanovich,
Inc. </p>

<hr>

<p align="center">To Richard Evans Schultes, Ph. D., M. H. (Hon.)
</p>

<p align="center">Pioneer Explorer of Psychotropic Plants in the
New World </p>

<p align="center">Holder of the Paul C. Mangelsdorf Chair in the
Natural Sciences </p>

<p align="center">Director and Curator of Economic Botany </p>

<p align="center">Botanical Museum of Harvard University </p>

